### ğŸ§  Typing

- Always type:
  - Route context (`Context<{ Bindings, Variables }>` if needed)
  - `req.valid()` returns
  - Handler return (`c.json<{ success: boolean, data: T }>`)

- Use Zod inference (`z.infer<typeof schema>`) to match types from `@repo/types`.

